    "description": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >概述</h2></strong><br>艾琳因犯下重罪被从天堂放逐，为了向天堂复仇，她拿起地狱中的武器，将要在这里掀起腥风血雨。<br>在游戏中，玩家将扮演艾琳在天堂中猎杀虚伪的恶魔，从他们身上收集符石碎片用于交换升级物品和强力的装备。使用近战武器进行流畅的砍杀，或是使用远程武器进行精准的打击，或用法术武器造成大范围伤害，您的战斗风格完全取决于您的选择。一步一步向前推进直到面临最终的首领，他将会在战斗中考验你所有的战斗技巧。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>符石就是力量</strong></h2>你可以收紧口袋，利用“利息”系统在前中期尽可能多地积累符石，并在后期花费符石来购买昂贵的强力的武器，但会让你前期的战斗这如同刀剑跳舞般危险。<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >超过30种多样的武器</h2></strong><br>武器基本可以分为近战武器，远程武器以及元素武器三大类。高等级的独特武器往往有独一无二的特性或战技。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224260/extras/632c01ca017639bac8e2821293fc3241.avif?t=1695389471\" width=538 height=1734 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224260/extras/abe32359d4f4ac82ef5e051870aba16e.poster.avif?t=1695389471\" width=344 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224260/extras/abe32359d4f4ac82ef5e051870aba16e.webm?t=1695389471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224260/extras/abe32359d4f4ac82ef5e051870aba16e.mp4?t=1695389471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224260/extras/f686356020ea251e1617768591f43bc8.poster.avif?t=1695389471\" width=344 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224260/extras/f686356020ea251e1617768591f43bc8.webm?t=1695389471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224260/extras/f686356020ea251e1617768591f43bc8.mp4?t=1695389471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224260/extras/6f6962a8b73185b410aacd555cd18deb.poster.avif?t=1695389471\" width=344 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224260/extras/6f6962a8b73185b410aacd555cd18deb.webm?t=1695389471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224260/extras/6f6962a8b73185b410aacd555cd18deb.mp4?t=1695389471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >花费符石购买升级</h2></strong><br>在游戏中，你可以花费符石来购买商店中的物品来提升属性，或者获得一个特殊效果来改变你的战斗风格。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224260/extras/831ce514bfee3744a79c2d0016ad74a3.poster.avif?t=1695389471\" width=344 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224260/extras/831ce514bfee3744a79c2d0016ad74a3.webm?t=1695389471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224260/extras/831ce514bfee3744a79c2d0016ad74a3.mp4?t=1695389471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >回火系统</h2></strong><br>每一种武器都有其独特的“性格”，用心感受武器的力量和节奏，在你和武器同步合拍的一瞬间按下“回火”，即可让武器爆发出其真正的威力。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224260/extras/9844cfbaa81ad49966abdd347b731bec.poster.avif?t=1695389471\" width=704 height=382 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224260/extras/9844cfbaa81ad49966abdd347b731bec.webm?t=1695389471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224260/extras/9844cfbaa81a